      "content": "wait, i dont have insurance here, i'm in london so i'd have to go to a private clinic if i dont want to wait at the a&e... i have some propranolol left over from my doctor for my anxiety, do you think if i take a couple of those it'll help calm my heart down and settle this feeling? i just really want to sleep it off if i can.",
